---
title: Field Notes
description: Daily field notes from the Volkman Farm homestead in Sanford, FL. Microgreens, homesteading, and permaculture in a Central Florida backyard.
pagination:
  data: collections.post
  size: 15
  reverse: true
  alias: entries
permalink: "/blog/{% if pagination.pageNumber > 0 %}page/{{ pagination.pageNumber | plus: 1 }}/{% endif %}"
eleventyComputed:
  title: "Field Notes{% if pagination.pageNumber > 0 %}, page {{ pagination.pageNumber | plus: 1 }}{% endif %}"
layout: default
---

<p class="lead">Notes from a Sanford backyard, most days of the week. Microgreens on the trays, a homestead taking shape around them, and permaculture doing the quiet work underneath.</p>

<ul class="post-list">
{% for post in entries %}
  <li>
    <p class="post-meta"><time datetime="{{ post.date | date: '%Y-%m-%d', 'America/New_York' }}">{{ post.date | date: "%B %-d, %Y", "America/New_York" }}</time>{% if post.data.pillar %} · {{ post.data.pillar }}{% endif %}</p>
    <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
    <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
  </li>
{% endfor %}
</ul>

{% if pagination.pages.size > 1 %}
<nav class="pager" aria-label="Field notes pages">
  {% if pagination.href.previous %}<a class="pager-prev" rel="prev" href="{{ pagination.href.previous }}">← Newer</a>{% endif %}
  <span class="pager-count">Page {{ pagination.pageNumber | plus: 1 }} of {{ pagination.pages.size }}</span>
  {% if pagination.href.next %}<a class="pager-next" rel="next" href="{{ pagination.href.next }}">Older →</a>{% endif %}
</nav>
{% endif %}
